The DataImportManager class handles the clearing and importing of data for medicines, patients, and staff.

Interface for managing medical records of patients.
Medicine

MedicineImportService is a service that implements the DataImportService interface for importing a list of Medicine entities from a CSV file.

Represents an action performed on the inventory of a specific medicine, detailing the quantity, type of action, date/time, administrator, and reason.

The MedicineRepository class is responsible for managing a collection of medicine records.
Patient

PatientController

PatientImportService is a service that implements the DataImportService interface to import patient data from a CSV file and convert it into a list of Patient entities.
PatientRepository
The PatientRepository class is responsible for managing a collection of patient records.

Interface for managing patient-related operations, including appointment handling, patient records, and doctor-patient interactions.

Represents a pharmacist in the system, responsible for dispensing medications and handling replenishment requests.

PrescriptionStatus
Enum representing the status of a prescription.
ReplenishmentRequest

ReplenishmentStatus
Enum representing the status of a replenishment request.
Repository<T,ID>

StaffImportService

StaffRepository
StaffRepository is a singleton class responsible for managing staff members, including both doctors and pharmacists.
Treatment
The Treatment class represents a medical treatment with a description.
User
The User class is an abstract base class that represents a user in the system.
UserRole
Enum representing the different roles a user can have in the system.
